message: Good afternoon, my name is Jamie. How can I help you today?
I'm really disappointed. This is the second time I’ve reached out because my withdrawal is too slow. Why is it taking so long?  Where's my money?
I'm truly sorry to hear you're experiencing delays. I completely understand how frustrating this must be. Let me look into it right away.
Before we continue, can you confirm your registered email address, date of birth, and the last four digits of your payment method for security purposes?
Thank you for verifying. Just to confirm, your withdrawal request of $250 is currently in the processing stage and should be finalized within 48 hours.
I was told 24 hours last time. This is getting ridiculous!
I sincerely apologize for any confusion and understand how important this is to you. To help resolve this, I'll escalate your case to our finance team for urgent review.
Alright, I hope this gets sorted soon.
Absolutely, we’ll do our best to speed things up for you. Thank you for your patience, and please don’t hesitate to reach out if you need further assistance.
